{"tid":957952,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友暪住我去玩free hug 我決定同佢分手","createTime":"2018-12-27T11:55:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T12:45:45.000Z","uid":38737,"like":8,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"08d95ec4a708ce1e2f4db4910f874bb2018470fd","tid":957952,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T11:55:59.000Z","msg":"講番少少背景先 我同女朋友係中學識既 中三開始拍拖 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去到中五我會考得8分去左讀ive 佢就27分去左恆商讀 之後仲升埋3大bba <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然係咁 但女朋友都冇捨我而去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去到今年聖誕節 我問老母拎錢出街 點知今次老母竟然唔比錢我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好在女朋友同我講唔緊要因為佢都要陪屋企人 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n於是今年平安夜我就係高登過啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點知個晚11點幾 收到中學同學 send sms比我(我冇whatsapp) <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢同我講見到我女朋友係尖沙咀拎住塊牌玩free hug <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲話有好多mk 毒撚排住隊攬佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我一開始都唔信 仲以為係人有相似 我就開玩笑咁問佢:喂 有人話見到你係尖沙咀玩free hug喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點知佢唔出聲 面色一沉咁 過左幾秒 佢:下..邊個見到..佢認錯人.. <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我就開始覺得唔對路 咪追問落去:係咪有姐 我又要攬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n半推半撞下 佢真係爆左出黎 話:我個fd話好好玩咪試下囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我聽到之後成個人灰哂 覺得女朋友轉變左好多 果陣佢仲天真無邪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家竟然做雞咁 我鬧佢係雞 竟然為左3蚊走去玩three hug <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢就話 : 係free hug,冇收錢架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我聽到就更加嬲 再鬧佢唔使錢比人攬 連雞都不如呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢就喊得好勁 我見到咁 就唔忍心話佢住 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n叫大家冷靜下先..<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c4dce852b33d8b95df97d910eaec1aa04d9118e","tid":957952,"uid":11598,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T11:56:27.000Z","msg":"free fuck"},{"pid":"7344404646e3c7e8332f0d31698e45f139e8264f","tid":957952,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c4dce852b33d8b95df97d910eaec1aa04d9118e","tid":957952,"uid":11598,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T11:56:27.000Z","msg":"free fuck"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T11:56:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f34151d752c5efbd7894bde44027cb3dd2cc6358","tid":957952,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7344404646e3c7e8332f0d31698e45f139e8264f","tid":957952,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c4dce852b33d8b95df97d910eaec1aa04d9118e","tid":957952,"uid":11598,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T11:56:27.000Z","msg":"free fuck"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T11:56:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T11:57:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3946128762ca434c4d4609ceca40919b722b9377","tid":957952,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T11:57:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a4ef5d5b0035227faa6dde43671a749915b0672b","tid":957952,"uid":208722,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T11:57:39.000Z","msg"